SCTX:
begin waterstate_torchenable

short initialized
short myheight
short enablestate



if ( initialized == 0 )
	set initialized to 1
	set myheight to GetPos Z
endif

if ( GetWaterLevel > myheight )
	if ( enablestate != 1 )
		Enable
		set enablestate to 1
		
	endif
else
	if ( enablestate != 2 )
		Disable
		set enablestate to 2
	
	endif
endif


end
